trans-unit.source: The source entity object and all entity objects passed in must be in an <xref:System.Data.EntityState> or <xref:System.Data.EntityState> state.
trans-unit.target: 원본 엔터티 개체가 및 전달 되는 모든 엔터티 개체에 있어야는 <xref:System.Data.EntityState>또는 <xref:System.Data.EntityState>상태.</xref:System.Data.EntityState> </xref:System.Data.EntityState>
